summary: Mask clouds by dilating Sen2Cor sceneclassification
description: Mask clouds by dilating Sen2Cor sceneclassification. This dilation algorithm removes pixels in the neighbourhood of clouds in a fairly aggresive manner, to avoid any type of contamination. Nevertheless, some outliers can sometimes still remain.

parameters.description: The source data cube containing Sentinel-2 input.
